messages.message: is anyone else still blocked on this? My same PR is still timing out today and I'm wondering whether I should look into other possible causes if the loadgen PR unblocked others
my CI builds have gotten a lot faster, are your CI builds still taking a long time?
ya so this CI test (https://jenkins.instabase.com/blue/organizations/jenkins/instabase/detail/PR-37049/16/pipeline/) went on for 2hrs, was yours hanging at a similar step/unit test folder?
@pauline.comising you can compare your test runs with successful ones and see if the successful one runs a test suite that your CI test doesnt. if there  is such one, that could help u narrow it down

i once wrote a unit test that relied on being able to execute a model in model service, but there is no model service running when jenkins runs ci/cd test so it made the unit test run forever and cause the build to timeout
ahh, ya so you mean comparing the list of these unit tests to find which folder didnt get marked as `[OK]` in mine and caused the time out in my PR
